<div id="user-switching">
<h1>Switching to another user</h1>
<p>The application allows Administrators to <b>switch</b> or <b>impersonate</b> any user in the system. Impersonating will replace your current
Administrator credentials with ones of selected user (including all their roles).</p>
<p>There are several ways to initiate impersonation:</p>
<ul>
	<li>From user listing</li>
	<li>User properties page</li>
	<li>Fast switch tool top right:
	<div id="assmem_username">
	<p>Start typing user's last name or first name. After list is loaded from server, select user from list and press &lt;Enter&gt; key.</p>
	</div>
	</li>
</ul>
<p class="help-img"><img src="../img/user-switched.png" /> Information on switched user displayed in title bar</p>
<p>Please note that any changes made to the data will record the createdBy or lastModified properties of records as <b>User/Impersonator</b> (e.g. <code>MObreza/Administrator</code>
where user Administrator is impersonating user MObreza).</p>

</div>
</body>
</html>